message: Dear Bob, I'm excited to present our premium product to you. This item holds significant value to me and I believe it would be a great addition to your collection. Considering its worth to both of us, I propose a price of $13,500 for this product. I am confident this offer strikes a balance between reflecting its true value and providing you with an attractive opportunity. Please let me know if you're interested in discussing further details or proceeding with the purchase.
